title: The footpath and highway:
author: Moran, Benjamin
snippet: The streets most deserving notice are Briggate, Xorth Street, Commercial Street, and Yv^ood-house Lane. The shops on the first named are quite imposing, and many of them are as tastefully  fitted up as those of London.
